<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN291-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai - atu; tuṟai - vēttiyal. neṭuṅkaḻuttup paraṇar.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>  
    <div xml:id="PN291">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>ciṟāaar tuṭiyar pāṭuvaṉ makāaar</l>
<l>tūveḷ ḷaṟuvai māyōṟ kuṟuki</l>
<l>yirumpuṭ pūca lōmpumiṉ yāṉum</l>
<l>viḷarik koṭpiṉ veṇṇari kaṭikuve</l>
<l>ṉeṉpōṟ peruvitup puṟuka vēntē</l>
<l>koṉṉuñ cātal veyyōṟkut taṉṟalai</l>
<l>maṇimaruṇ mālai cūṭṭi yavaṉṟalai</l>
<l>orukāḻ mālai tāṉmalain taṉaṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Boys, drummers, folks capable of singing,</l>
<l>go near the dark man with a pure white cloth</l>
<l>and protect [him] from the clamour of the dark birds. I too</l>
<l>will chase away the white jackals with tours of Viḷari.</l>
<l>Like me, please make great haste, king.</l>
<l>Putting on his own head the sapphire-like [Nocci] garland</l>
<l>of him who was keen on dying in vain he</l>
<l>put on his head a garland with one strand.  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
